Package: bcsapps
Title: Create a shiny app project using BCStats standards
Version: 0.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Stephanie",
           family = "Yurchak",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "Stephanie.Yurchak@gov.bc.ca")
Description: This package uses bcgovr::create_bcgov_project to set up an RProject with
           all the files necessary to comply with bc gov standards and then also 
           adds in the files needed for a basic BCStats shiny app.
